      "description": "Affected lines:\r\nFranklin/Foxboro Line",
      "severity": 1,
      "route_id": "unknown"
    },
    {
      "id": "1021672",
      "title": "",
      "description": "Beginning July 13, 2026, the Woburn Anderson Regional Transportation Center will undergo a major paving and infrastructure improvement project, with work expected to be completed by November 16, 2026. \r\n\r\nTo support these critical renovations and enhance the long-term safety and functionality of the facility, select areas of the MBTA Daily Lot and the gated Overnight Lot will be temporarily closed throughout the construction period.\r\n\r\nMotorists and facility users are encouraged to plan accordingly and carefully follow all posted signage, traffic control measures, and parking restrictions to ensure a safe and efficient experience during the project.",
      "severity": 8,
      "route_id": "unknown"
    },
